-------
Install
-------
git clone https://github.com/dickmao/emacs-ghostty.git
make -C emacs-ghostty install

-----
Usage
-----
C-y pastes from the shell's kill ring (subsequent M-y from same).

C-c C-y pastes from emacs's kill ring (subsequent M-y from same).

C-c C-y also exits tmux-like copy mode to paste a just copied region.

Any "normal typing" (non-prefixed) key exits tmux-like copy mode.

C-p immediately enters tmux-like copy mode.

M-v immediately enters tmux-like copy mode.
